      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the atmosphere, but it feels a bit generic. I want to get more specific with the \"tension\" part. Can you add some details about the people you might see hanging out on the street corners or walking through these alleys? I want to capture the specific \"vibe\" of the people who live there to make the danger feel more real and grounded. What kind of characters would make this place feel truly intimidating?",
